# CNAME File Example
# ==================
# 
# To use a custom domain instead of github.io:
# 1. Copy this file to "CNAME" (without the .example extension)
# 2. Replace "yourdomain.com" with your actual domain
# 3. Update your DNS records with your domain provider
#
# Example for custom domain:
# yourdomain.com
#
# Example for subdomain:
# www.yourdomain.com
#
# DNS Records to add:
# Type: CNAME
# Name: www
# Value: YOUR_USERNAME.github.io
#
# Type: A
# Name: @
# Value: 185.199.108.153
# Value: 185.199.109.153  
# Value: 185.199.110.153
# Value: 185.199.111.153
#
# Note: Wait 24-48 hours for DNS propagation after updating records.